cng bng v hp l ty theo nng lc ca mi ngi trn mi phng din: tuyn dng, o to, b nhim, xt lng, xt thng &#8230;vv. Chng ti to ra mt trng lm vic nng ng v cng bng cho ngi lao ng, l ni mi ngi u c c hi lm vic, rn luyn  hon thin bn thn. </p>\r\n                                    <p>Cng ty TNHH Jia Hsin lun t ho v mi trng lm vic chuyn nghip, nng ng nhng cng v cng thn thin v m m. Lm vic ti Cng ty, bn s cm thy mnh nh thnh vin ca mt i gia nh y p nim tin v hy vng, lun c quan tm, chia s v cng nhau cng hin, pht huy nhng gi tr bn thn  xy dng ngi nh chung Cng ty ngy cng ln mnh. Jia Hsin s l mi nh th hai ca CB-CNV.</p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                                <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns\">\r\n                                    <img src=\"http://jiahsin.dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/IMG_5906.jpg\" />\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"small-12 medium-6 large-6 columns\">\r\n                                    <img src=\"http://jiahsin.dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/IMG_6155.jpg\" />\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </section>\r\n\r\n                        <section id=\"recruitment-policies\">\r\n                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                                <div class=\"column\">\r\n                                    <h3>CHNH SCH TUYN DNG</h3>\r\n                                    <p>Cng ty chng ti tuyn dng da trn nng lc c nhn, kinh nghim lm vic, kin thc ph hp v p ng c nhu cu ca Cng ty.</p>\r\n                                    <p>Vi quan im coi ngun nhn lc l li th cnh tranh hng u ca Cng ty, nguyn tc tuyn dng ca Cng ty l la chn nhng ng vin tt nht vo v tr ph hp da trn phm cht, kh nng, thi , nng lc, kinh nghim ca ng vin m khng phn bit tn ngng, chng tc, tn gio hay gii tnh. Cng ty u tin cc ng vin c kinh nghim trong ngnh giy dp v ngun nhn lc a phng. </p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </section>\r\n\r\n                        <section id=\"training-policies\">\r\n                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                                <div class=\"large-3 columns\">\r\n                                    <h3>Chnh sch o to</h3>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"large-4 columns\">\r\n                                    <p>Cng ty Jia Hsin lun coi o to Ngun nhn lc l nhim v quan trng hng u trong cng tc qun l Ngun nhn lc v l mt hnh thc u t chin lc ca cng ty. Thng qua vic o to, CB-CNV s c nng cao kin thc, trnh  nghip v chuyn mn cng cc k nng khc, t  to ra gi tr ln nht cho bn thn nhn vin v Cng ty. ng thi, qua qu trnh o to, CB-CNV cng xc nh c mc tiu pht trin ca bn thn ph hp vi mc tiu pht trin ca Cng ty.</p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"large-5 columns\">\r\n                                    <p>Cc kha o to s c thit k mt cch hiu qu da trn yu cu thc tin kinh doanh ca Cng ty nhm m bo vic CB-CNV c th p dng c ti a nhng k nng, kin thc  c o to vo trong cng vic. T , lm tng nim tin v ng lc lm vic cho CB-CNV, thc y CB-CNV khng ngng pht trin v a dng ha ngh nghip chuyn mn  to ra c hi thng tin cho bn thn. Do  cng ty chng ti lun khuyn khch CB-CNV ch ng trong hc tp v pht trin ngh nghip ca bn thn. </p>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </section>\r\n\r\n                        <section id=\"wage-benefits\">\r\n                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n                                <div class=\"medium-12 large-3 columns\">\r\n                                    <h3>Ch <span>lng thng &#038; phc li</span></h3>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div class=\"medium-