(115, 1, '2019-10-17 02:06:42', '2019-10-17 02:06:42', '	<div id=\"content\" class=\"site-content\">\r\n	    <section id=\"banner\">\r\n	        <div class=\"full-width\">\r\n	            <div class=\"bxslider\" id=\"slider-453\">\r\n	                <div><img src=\"http://www.jiahsin.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5877.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	                <div><img src=\"http://www.jiahsin.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5722.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	                <div><img src=\"http://www.jiahsin.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5709.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	                <div><img src=\"http://www.jiahsin.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5684.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	                <div><img src=\"http://www.jiahsin.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_5646.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	            </div>\r\n	        </div>\r\n	        <div class=\"overlay\"></div>\r\n	    </section>\r\n	    <div class=\"site-content-wrapper\">\r\n\r\n\r\n	        <div id=\"primary\" class=\"content-area\">\r\n	            <main id=\"main\" class=\"site-main\" role=\"main\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	                <article id=\"post-11\" class=\"post-11 page type-page status-publish hentry\">\r\n	                    <header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n	                        <h1 class=\"entry-title\">Trch nhim x hi</h1>\r\n	                    </header><!-- .entry-header -->\r\n\r\n	                    <div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n	                        <div class=\"page-subtitle\">\r\n	                            <h2>Trch nhim x hi</h2>\r\n	                            <div>Pht trin sn xut kinh doanh ca cng ty khng th tch ri pht trin bn vng</div>\r\n	                        </div>\r\n	                        <section id=\"general-approach\">\r\n	                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n	                                <div class=\"column\">\r\n	                                    <h3>Trch Nhim X Hi v Pht Trin Bn Vng ti Jia Hsin</h3>\r\n	                                    <p>Trong hn 20 nm hot ng, chng ti nhn ra rng  gt hi nhiu thnh cng hn na trong kinh doanh, chng ti cn phi phi p ng c tt c cc mi quan tm t pha khch hng, ch u t, cn b cng nhn vin, chnh ph, cng ng a phng v mi trng xung quanh bng cc hot ng c trch nhim cao v o c i vi x hi. Trch nhim x hi v pht trin bn vng  c tch hp vo tt c cc hot ng sn xut kinh doanh. Mi CBCNV u  thc c vai tr v trch nhim ca mnh trong vic chung tay cng Ban Lnh o to ra mi trng lm vic an ton, lnh mnh, mang li li ch cho c i bn, gi gn mi trng xanh sch v ng gp cho s pht trin ca cng ng a phng.</p>\r\n	                                </div>\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                        </section>\r\n	                        <section id=\"lsc-csrd\">\r\n	                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n	                                <div class=\"small-12 medium-12 large-5 columns\">\r\n	                                    <h3>Hi ng Bo H Lao ng &#038; B phn Trch Nhim X Hi</h3>\r\n	                                    <p>B phn Trch Nhim X Hi l b phn chuyn trch v cc cng tc trch nhim x hi v mi trng ca cng ty. H tr cho b phn Trch Nhim X Hi l Hi ng Bo H Lao ng, bao gm cc thnh vin l cc cn b qun l t cc b phn phn xng. Ngoi cng vic sn xut kinh doanh hng ngy, cc thnh vin ca Hi ng Bo H Lao ng cng cam kt thc hin tt cc nhim v v an ton lao ng, bo v mi trng, chm lo cho quyn li ca CBCNV v thc hin cc hot ng x hi cng ng. Nu cc chnh sch &#038; mc tiu v trch nhim x hi v pht trin bn vng tc ng n hot ng sn xut kinh doanh, cc thnh vin s cn i gia hai lnh vc nhm mang n kt qu tt p nht cho cng ty. </p>\r\n	                                </div>\r\n	                                <div class=\"small-12 medium-12 large-5 columns\">\r\n	                                    <img src=\"http://www.jiahsin.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/hdbhldtnxh.png\" />\r\n	                                </div>\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"row\" id=\"functions\">\r\n	                                <h4>Chc nng v nhim v</h4>\r\n	                                <ul class=\"medium-block-grid-3 large-block-grid-5\">\r\n	                                    <li>\r\n	                                        <h6>Tham mu</h6>Tham mu, h tr cho Ban Tng Gim c trong vic t chc thc hin v kim tra, gim st vic thc hin cc chng trnh trch nhim x hi &#038; pht trin bn vng ca ton cng ty.\r\n	                                    </li>\r\n	                                    <li>\r\n	                                        <h6>Xy dng ni quy</h6>Xy dng ni quy, quy ch, quy trnh, bin php tt nht cho hot ng trch nhim x hi &#038; pht trin bn vng ca cng ty.\r\n	                                    </li>\r\n	                                    <li>\r\n	                                        <h6>Lp k hoch</h6>Xy dng k hoch hot ng hng nm, n c, gim st vic thc hin k hoch, nh gi cc ri ro v xy dng cc k hoch ng cu, i ph khn cp.\r\n	                                    </li>\r\n	                                    <li>\r\n	                                        <h6>T chc</h6>T chc thc hin cc hot ng tuyn truyn, ph bin cc quy nh ca cng ty v trch nhim x hi cho ton th cng nhn vin bit.\r\n	                                    </li>\r\n	                                    <li>\r\n	                                        <h6> xut</h6> xut vi Ban Tng Gim c cc bin php sa sai khc phc (nu c)\r\n	                                    </li>\r\n	                                </ul>\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                        </section>\r\n	                        <section id=\"sustainability-strategy\">\r\n	                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n	                                <div class=\"column\">\r\n	                                    <h3>Chin lc<span>pht trin bn vng</span></h3>\r\n	                                </div>\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n	                                <div class=\"small-12 medium-12 large-5 columns\">\r\n	                                    <p>Pht trin bn vng l mc tiu khng tch ri trong mi hot ng ca cng ty chng ti. Chng ti chu trch nhim cho s pht trin lu bn ca cng ty, ton th cn b cng nhn vin cng nh mi trng sng v cng ng a phng xung quanh cng ty. </p>\r\n	                                    <p>Chin lc pht trin bn vng ca cng ty bao gm 3 yu t nn tng chnh: </p>\r\n	                                    <ul>\r\n	                                        <li>Thc thi s mnh v tm nhn ca cng ty</li>\r\n	                                        <li>Tun th cc yu cu php lut v cc chun mc ph bin hin hnh;</li>\r\n	                                        <li>p ng cc k vng v yu cu ca cc bn lin quan quan trng;</li>\r\n	                                    </ul>\r\n	                                    <p>Da trn nn tng chin lc ny, chng ti  xy dng cc h thng qun l, cc chnh sch v quy trnh, thc hin cc chng trnh v d n, nh gi sot xt v thc thi ci tin lin tc. </p>\r\n	                                </div>\r\n	                                <div class=\"small-12 medium-12 large-6 columns\">\r\n	                                    <img src=\"http://www.jiahsin.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/strategy-vi.png\" />\r\n	                                </div>\r\n	                            </div>\r\n	                            <div class=\"row\">\r\n	                                <div class=\"column\" id=\"results\">\r\n	                                    <h5>Thnh qu</h5>\r\n	                                    <ul class=\"small-block-grid-1 medium-block-grid-2 large-block-grid-4\">\r\n	                                        <li>\r\n	                                            <h6>Khch hng</h6>t c s tn nhim cao ca khch hng. Vn  trch nhim x hi &#038; pht trin bn vng lun c khch hng u tin trong nguyn tc hot ng ca h.\r\n	                                        </li>\r\n	                                        <li>\r\n	                                            <h6>